    "description": "《Police Station Simulator》是一款在一间年久失修的警察局里完成大面积翻新以及诸多不起眼的工作的游戏。<br><br>开心小镇的镇长派你去重启一个破败不堪的警察局。你的任务就是让它重现昔日的辉煌。有信心胜完成这个任务吗？又或是让双猪镇就此告别警察局呢？<br><br>备好咖啡和甜甜圈吧，前面有很多工作等着你呢！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/d466424ca472b874773c16e18a25d0e3.poster.avif?t=1768214687\" width=600 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/d466424ca472b874773c16e18a25d0e3.webm?t=1768214687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>因年久失修，警察局的角落里满目疮痍。需要收拾垃圾、擦地板、更换破旧的陈设等。唤醒你内心的完美主义，尽心竭力地打扫一番，让整个空间比刚擦过的警徽还闪亮如新！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/fb8c36aac7c743fdb123ee8d2c094193.poster.avif?t=1768214687\" width=600 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/fb8c36aac7c743fdb123ee8d2c094193.webm?t=1768214687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>查看可用的雇员，聘用具备合适要求（或预算）的技能的人员。他们会在你的培养下快速地独当一面吗？还是会一个又一个地疯掉呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/21716fb82f727e5c2d5cdf7cbeaa3585.poster.avif?t=1768214687\" width=600 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/21716fb82f727e5c2d5cdf7cbeaa3585.webm?t=1768214687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>听取犯罪报告，快速立案，并派警员去侦办。给警队配备适用的警具，确保所有的警车行动前车况良好。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/aafc0fe07f4fb5aa74d3c378806ca1d6.poster.avif?t=1768214687\" width=600 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/aafc0fe07f4fb5aa74d3c378806ca1d6.webm?t=1768214687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>警员们如果能同吃在一起，就能团结一致去完成任务！给警员分发甜甜圈和咖啡，在解决最麻烦的案件时保持士气高涨。保持警员们的工作环境整洁、安全，可能的话也请提供一些娱乐活动给他们。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/7805b41b12f65b06375217e67f4b8405.poster.avif?t=1768214687\" width=600 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/7805b41b12f65b06375217e67f4b8405.webm?t=1768214687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>打印、填表、签字、盖章，不断地重复。为了最大限度地利用开心小镇镇长批复的资金，你得保证每件来之不易的成功事件之后都有据可查。镇长常说：务必专款专用！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/7f949541b7c9ac830f5df6977c6966be.poster.avif?t=1768214687\" width=600 height=235 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2155140/extras/7f949541b7c9ac830f5df6977c6966be.webm?t=1768214687\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>获得资金后你可以扩建警察局，同时可解锁侦办更复杂的案件所需要的新功能。<br>......或者你也可以把钱都花在华丽的装饰上，把墙都重新刷成粉色 - 你可以毫无顾忌地花公家的拨款。<br><br>你才是游戏的主宰，随心所欲地尽情享受它带给你的快乐吧。开心小镇的警察部队随时听候您的调遣！",
